section.section:
"Child care center" does not include:
a nonpublic kindergarten in which an instructional program is offered or provided for children who are at least 5 years old;
a nonpublic elementary school in which an instructional program is offered or provided for children who are in grades 1 through 8;
a child care home, a child care institution, or other child care facility that offers or provides a residential placement for a child and is established, licensed, or registered under this subtitle, Title 9 of the Human Services Article, or Title 10 of the Health - General Article; or
a family child care home or large family child care home that is required to be registered or is registered under this subtitle.
